### 2) Send message to AI chat channel
POST http://localhost:8082/api/chat/AI/user123-tictactoe
Authorization: Bearer {{chat_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Hoe speel ik tic tac toe?"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("ai_reference", "user123-tictactoe");
%}

### 3) Send second message to AI channel
POST http://localhost:8082/api/chat/AI/{{ai_reference}}
Authorization: Bearer {{chat_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Wat is de beste openingszet?"
}

### 4) GET AI chat messages
GET http://localhost:8082/api/chat/AI/{{ai_reference}}
Authorization: Bearer {{chat_token}}

### 5) GET AI chat messages since timestamp
GET http://localhost:8082/api/chat/AI/{{ai_reference}}?since=2025-01-01T00:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer {{chat_token}}

